---
import { SITE } from "../config";
---

<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 sm:px-10 py-[clamp(4rem,10vh,8rem)]">
  <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_240px] lg:gap-16 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]">
    <!-- Text column -->
    <div>
      <p class="kicker reveal mb-5">About</p>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">
        Full stack, all the way to the <span class="text-[var(--color-aurora)]">cloud</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="reveal-blur mt-7 space-y-5 leading-[1.75] text-[var(--color-body)]" style="--d:120ms">
        <p>
          I'm {SITE.name.split(" ")[0]}, a software engineer in {SITE.location}. For the past two years
          I've designed and shipped web apps end to end. Most recently a
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">modular ERP platform</strong>, built with Django
          and React and used in production across several departments.
        </p>

        <p>
          What I enjoy most is owning the whole stack, down to the infrastructure. I run apps on AWS,
          containerise them with Docker and orchestrate with Kubernetes; and as an
          <strong class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">RHCE and CCNA</strong>, deployment and
          reliability aren't an afterthought. Lately that's meant building AI products too, like EduFlow
          (an LMS with a Llama&nbsp;3.3 tutor) and ResumeAI. Everything in the projects below is live, so click
          through and try it.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you're hiring, building an MVP, or just curious about something here, I'd genuinely like to
          hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo sidebar — only visible on lg+ -->
    <aside class="reveal hidden lg:block lg:pt-20" style="--d:200ms">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-3 rounded-3xl bg-[oklch(0.55_0.12_162/0.25)] blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <img
          src={SITE.photo}
          alt={`${SITE.name}, ${SITE.role} in Bangalore`}
          width="340"
          height="340"
          loading="lazy"
          class="relative aspect-square w-full rounded-3xl border border-[oklch(0.8_0.165_162/0.35)] object-cover"
        />
        <div class="hud mt-4 space-y-1.5">
          <p>RHCE · EX294 // CISCO CCNA</p>
          <p>M.TECH RVCE · BANGALORE</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
